name: No. 11 (Purple Stripes Over Green Panes)
description:
Part of a collection of hand-made color field items, this piece is a doorway to a New World.

The glowing green light that transpires from three horizontal panes invites the soul of the viewer to walk into a new dimension. On top, horizontal lines gently blend with the shapes underneath uniting the flow from silence to noise and from energy to stillness. 

It is the space of the New, therefore of the Unknown, where the chattering finally fades away and what is left is all the silence and all the potential dissonance of the universe.
